{"tid":543301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【桌球】傅家俊左眼視網膜退化 已接受激光手術 將休戰數月","createTime":"2018-01-28T10:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T14:02:06.000Z","uid":38737,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"3feadafb323cbf0efa4ee86a47b31b9684353b8f","tid":543301,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"Marco Fu 傅家俊<br />\n4 hrs &middot; <br />\n【特別宣佈】今季係我踏入職業生涯嘅20週年，對我嚟講係好重要嘅一年。今日，我要向大家宣佈一個消息。由於早前眼部出現不適，經醫生檢查及診斷後，確定左眼的視網膜退化。惟大家不用擔心，我已接受激光手術，醫生建議暫時讓眼部休息。因此，嚟緊幾個月，我將不會參與任何賽事。抱歉暫不接受訪問，日內將安排會見各傳媒，謝謝各位關心。<br />\n<br />\n2018 is an important year for me personally as this is my 20th anniversary as a pro snooker player. Today, I would like to share an update with you. Since the beginning of the season, I have been having some problems with my left eye. I was told by the doctor that I&rsquo;m suffering from retinal degeneration, laser surgery's been done so no worries! The doctor recommends a rest to avoid retinal detachment. Therefore I will not take part in any competition for the coming months. I regret to tell you that no interviews will be taken for now and I shall arrange an online session to take questions in the near future. Thank you for your support!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marcofuofficial/videos/808979252626916/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarcofuofficial%2Fvideos%2F808979252626916%2F&d=5DDn6lKicMIujhLNYaocQwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f173b82d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marcofuofficial/videos/808979252626916/</a><br />\n<br />\n-6<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6fe0b85f11e7eaed785f0d60a8f86dd0589a92","tid":543301,"uid":151324,"like":8,"dislike":34,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"繼歌手之後又可以轉行盲人按摩"},{"pid":"780c8f7f339e4dddc86ef66f8fc8a423bfb0369d","tid":543301,"ui